review.content: I would never wear this bra to anything but a low impact class like yoga. There's zero support and absolutely no modesty. Was hoping for better!

review.title: Not for high impact
review.content: Definitely not good for anything high-impact, but it's very stylish for yoga or something else low impact.

review.title: A regular or me
review.content: This is in regular rotation at the gym. Its colorful and looks kinda cute under my exercise tanks.

review.title: Great fit - love the v-neck design!
review.content: Great fit - love the v-neck design!

review.title: The seams bother me
review.content: Some of the seams bother me during certain workouts but otherwise very comfortable

review.title: A sweet n sporty look for the gym
review.content: Always a sweet n sporty look for the gym! Keeps me cool and the seams don't rub up against me like some of my other tanks.

review.title: Good choice for working out
review.content: Good choice for working out and stylin' enough to wear when I'm hanging with friends on hot days. Also washes really well!

review.title: I love the look
review.content: I love the look of this top, but I wasn't too crazy about the fit. The medium was too big in my opinion.

review.title: Huge arm holes??
review.content: I don't know why the arm holes are so big. It looked ok in the photo but in person they're really wide. It's really comfortable but that bugs me.

review.title: Super cute!!! I love it
review.content: Super cute!!! I love it and want more colors. I really like running in this tank because it's not too tight.
